<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>A Letter for Afifa</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(180deg,#020617,#071b35,#0f172a);
color:white;
}

#stars{
position:fixed;
width:100%;
height:100%;
overflow:hidden;
}

.star{
position:absolute;
width:2px;
height:2px;
background:white;
border-radius:50%;
animation:twinkle 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes twinkle{
50%{opacity:.2;}
}

.container{

width:92%;
max-width:760px;
padding:45px;
border-radius:25px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);

backdrop-filter:blur(14px);

text-align:center;

box-shadow:0 0 35px rgba(0,0,0,.45);

z-index:10;

}

.hidden{

display:none;

}

button{

margin-top:30px;

padding:15px 35px;

border:none;

border-radius:40px;

background:#3b82f6;

color:white;

font-size:18px;

cursor:pointer;

transition:.3s;

}

button:hover{

transform:scale(1.08);

}

.fade{

animation:fade .8s;

}

@keyframes fade{

from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(20px);
}

to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}

}

.typing{

overflow:hidden;

white-space:nowrap;

width:0;

border-right:2px solid white;

animation:typing 4s steps(40,end) forwards;

}

@keyframes typing{

from{width:0;}

to{width:100%;}

}

#count{

font-size:80px;

font-weight:bold;

color:#FFD54F;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div id="stars"></div>

<div class="container">

<div id="page1">

<h2>Preparing Something Special...</h2>

<div id="count">5</div>

</div>

<div id="page2" class="hidden fade">

<h1 class="typing">

Assalamu Alaikum, Afifa 🌸

</h1>

<br><br>

<p>

This isn't a gift.

It's simply a small page

filled with respect,

sincere prayers,

and good wishes.

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(3)">

Continue →

</button>

</div>

<div id="page3" class="hidden fade">

<h2>A Small Thought 🌿</h2>

<p>

Every person leaves an impression

in someone's life.

Some inspire through words.

Some through actions.

And some simply through

their kindness.

I hope you always remain

one of those people.

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(4)">

Next →

</button>

</div>
<div id="page4" class="hidden fade">

<h2>🤲 A Prayer For You</h2>

<p>

I sincerely pray that Allah grants you
peace in your heart,
strength in every hardship,
wisdom in every decision,
and barakah in every step you take.

May every sincere dua you make
find its way to acceptance.

Ameen.

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(5)">

Continue 🌙

</button>

</div>

<div id="page5" class="hidden fade">

<h2>🌸 A Gentle Reminder</h2>

<p>

Life won't always be easy.

But remember...

Every hardship carries wisdom.

Every delay has a purpose.

Every sincere effort
is known to Allah.

Keep believing.

Keep growing.

Keep smiling.

</p>

<button onclick="nextPage(6)">

One Last Page 💙

</button>

</div>

<div id="page6" class="hidden fade">

<h1>✨ Before You Leave...</h1>

<br>

<p style="line-height:2">

I won't ask you to remember me.

<br><br>

<b>

I'll just try to become
someone worth remembering.

</b>

<br><br>

Some memories don't ask to stay;

they simply find a place
in the heart.

🌿

<br><br>

May Allah always protect you,
guide you,
and bless your life
with happiness,
peace,
and endless barakah.

Ameen. 🤲

<br><br>

— With Respect

</p>

</div>

</div>

<script>

const stars=document.getElementById("stars");

for(let i=0;i<180;i++){

let s=document.createElement("div");

s.className="star";

s.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";

s.style.top=Math.random()*100+"vh";

s.style.animationDelay=Math.random()*2+"s";

stars.appendChild(s);

}

let count=5;

let timer=setInterval(()=>{

count--;

document.getElementById("count").innerHTML=count;

if(count==0){

clearInterval(timer);

page1.classList.add("hidden");

page2.classList.remove("hidden");

}

},1000);

function nextPage(n){

for(let i=2;i<=6;i++){

document.getElementById("page"+i).classList.add("hidden");

}

document.getElementById("page"+n).classList.remove("hidden");

}

</script>

</body>

</html>
